 237:Utilities/sequencer/stm32_seq.c ****      * TaskMask that comes from UTIL_SEQ_PauseTask() / UTIL_SEQ_ResumeTask
 238:Utilities/sequencer/stm32_seq.c ****      * SuperMask that comes from UTIL_SEQ_Run
 239:Utilities/sequencer/stm32_seq.c ****      * If the waited event is there, exit from  UTIL_SEQ_Run() to return to the
